{"tid":982181,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"到底我地bees 何去何從","createTime":"2019-01-15T02:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T09:01:59.000Z","uid":14739,"like":1,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c4bb996264f55722859f0514eb3962e5d979f5b0","tid":982181,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"我同一個朋友就創立咗一個牌子 Bees<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n靈感就係來自一首詩 《蜂》<br />\n詩中有一句 採得百花成蜜後 為誰辛苦為誰甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好比現今社會 人類就好似工具一樣 做緊一啲對自己無意義嘅工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成就緊其他人 然後一生就咁虛耗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古人一千幾年前嘅反省 估唔到 一千幾百年過去 好似仍然存在緊呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁目前就整咗第一個系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ponV5YH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FponV5YH.jpg&h=6d69c78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qce11gq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQce11gq.jpg&h=da5f3302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSLTSpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSLTSpN.jpg&h=a613c8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g23aUC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg23aUC8.jpg&h=c76c5e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就喺呢度順便講下我地遇過嘅挫折啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於我地兩個一個住北區 一個住九龍西 真好難成日見面去傾 之後我地膽粗粗租左個臨時辦公室開始左我地嘅夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n設計 布料 同廠家磋商 到成品 擺貨地方 全部都要我地去面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到呢度諗住已經踏入大直路 只能說少年 太年輕鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地同第一個廠商整左數十件成品出來 結果不如理想 要報銷 真係深受打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地依然無放棄到 繼續去聯絡第二個廠家 結果又遇到困難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為對方要求我地一個款式最少要幾百件 佢地先會起貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對於兩個剛剛撞板嘅傻仔 再要我地投放更多資金 真係好大風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我地掙扎左好耐 覺得值得博多一次 就決定去馬 結果就真係出左一批我地滿意嘅成品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/685Qasd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F685Qasd.jpg&h=cdc0f877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46pJvf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46pJvf8.jpg&h=d2f3c823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pG1LJA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpG1LJA9.jpg&h=f602a956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32SZN2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32SZN2R.jpg&h=a36fab73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 我地覺得賣出街 首先要過到我地自己 所以第一批我地選擇報銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n件衫設計上都有啲特點 而且呢兩個月黎都發生左好多故事 如果有興趣再問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢合理 質料唔錯 希望大家支持下本地品牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後希望大家可以FOLLOW IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bees_official2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbees_official2018%2F&d=SapV93%2BIpUVg07QGamfIC%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d22d3948\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/bees_official2018/</a><br />\n網站:<a href=\"https://beesfashionhk.wixsite.com/mysite-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeesfashionhk.wixsite.com%2Fmysite-1&d=SapV93%2BIpUVg07QGamfIC%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b372728a\" target=\"_blank\">https://beesfashionhk.wixsite.com/mysite-1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屬於我地連登時代既product"},{"pid":"8db751a573cc0dcbde66c38101032564488c344b","tid":982181,"uid":148874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T02:03:17.000Z","msg":"夜啦 收皮啦"},{"pid":"302f0dc3b5d3dada20c1a58abd99a7c5f7ba304e","tid":982181,"uid":181905,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:00:59.000Z","msg":"我寧願去U記買件剩色著都唔想著你地件野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚柒"},{"pid":"122c396e957db91cf3b6176480c5949a80508e15","tid":982181,"uid":4559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:08:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad73d7563f42dfeb2eb88c2daebfd52e0d3472ab","tid":982181,"uid":72343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"件衫設計上都有啲特點?<br />\n憑你地啲圖真係睇唔出, 咪又係得個濕鳩圖案係心口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同朱古力啲hoodies一鳩樣, 又話同BTS21 小丸子 melody合作乜乜柒柒, 結果求鳩其整個大頭樣係心口就賣你$3XX 狗也不屌"},{"pid":"6f261d7c4073f6d9bc9fc1e8b3966ad8a028bd40","tid":982181,"uid":129225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"又鞭"},{"pid":"eeac780b6a26c08bfbbfa072eb1b0d80c61d32a1","tid":982181,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:01:47.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd88306804d297b0e556b0f32c92fc473f9d923","tid":982181,"uid":138040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"What are you doing son?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9dad9639f810495fd4fbb84c118c9546827dcf","tid":982181,"uid":20368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"樓上咁多人未睇過？"},{"pid":"1f128926421c4cb32a61d08efff4b